data.name: Venom Swamp
data.desc: During each player's End Phase: Place 1 Venom Counter on each face-up monster, except "Venom" monsters. Monsters lose 500 ATK for each Venom Counter on them. Destroy a monster if its ATK becomes 0 by this effect.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Collection 2: The Duel Academy Years Mega Pack
